  <title><code>xdoc</code> extensions</title>

  <para xml:id="first-para">The <emphasis role="bold"><code>{$component-name}</code></emphasis> component uses (a subset of) <link
      xlink:href="https://docbook.org/" role="newpage">DocBook&#160;5.1</link> as its main vocabulary. Within this there can be so-called
        <emphasis><code>xdoc</code> extensions</emphasis>).</para>

  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para><code>xdoc</code> extensions are specific elements in the <code>xdoc</code> (<code>http://www.xtpxlib.nl/ns/xdoc</code>) namespace. These
        are described in <xref linkend="sect-available-xdoc-extension-elements"/>.</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>

